{"lemma": "عَزِيمَةٌ", "slug": "عَزِيمَةٌ", "root": "ع.ز.م", "root_slug": "ع-ز-م", "root_link": "/words/roots/ع-ز-م", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 1, "pos_tags": ["noun"], "has_etymology": true, "sense_count": 2}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n29010"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B2%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "determination", "fa": "عزم", "ur": "عزم", "tr": "azim", "id": "tekad", "bn": "দৃঢ়তা", "es": "determinación", "fr": "détermination", "de": "Entschlossenheit", "ru": "решимость", "zh": "决心"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "noun", "gloss": "verbal noun of عَزَمَ (ʕazama) (form I)", "tags": ["form-of", "noun-from-verb"]}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "determination"}]}, "etymology": {"source": "wiktextract", "text": "Verbal noun of عَزَمَ (ʕazama)."}, "ipa": ["/ʕa.ziː.ma/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n29010", "headword_ar": "عَزِيمَةٌ", "root": "Ezm", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "an inf. n. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eazama", "text_ar": "عَزَمَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the sense first expl. above. (S, K.) [As a simple subst., it signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Determination, resolution, decision,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fixed purpose of the mind;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazomN", "text_ar": "عَزْمٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazomapN", "text_ar": "عَزْمَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": or] the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "disposition and subjection of the mind to the wish,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thing desired:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ham p. 336:) or it is a subst. [signifying the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "making an affair to have,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "take, effect;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "settling it firmly;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Eazama", "text_ar": "عَزَمَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlA^amora", "text_ar": "الاَمْرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^amoDaAhu", "text_ar": "اَمْضَاهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHokamahu", "text_ar": "اَحْكَمَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": or, as in the Mj, the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "settling,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "determining, the heart,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mind, firmly upon the thing that one desires to do;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazomN", "text_ar": "عَزْمٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": or, accord. to El-Ghooree, ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazomN", "text_ar": "عَزْمٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "preceding desire to dispose and subject the mind to the act."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Har p. 3.) [The pl., in all the senses, is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazaAy^imu", "text_ar": "عَزَايِمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". Hence,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ai$otad~ati AlEazaAy^imu", "text_ar": "اِشْتَدَّتِ العَزَايِمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The determinations"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazamaAt", "text_ar": "عَزَمَات"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ")"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the commanders in the hostile and plundering expedition to distant parts, and their taking to them, became strong."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA. [Probably from a trad.]) ―         -b2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazomapN", "text_ar": "عَزْمَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in two places. ―         -b3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazaAy^imu A@ll~`hi", "text_ar": "عَزَايِمُ ا@للّٰهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The obligatory statutes"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ordinances of God:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, Msb, K, TA:) sing."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaziymapN", "text_ar": "عَزِيمَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (Msb.) ―         -b4-  And, accord. to Er-Rághib,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EaziymapN", "text_ar": "عَزِيمَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A charming;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taEowiy*N", "text_ar": "تَعْوِيذٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; as though thou imaginedst thy having imposed an obligation [thereby] upon the devil, lest [for"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AY", "text_ar": "اى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in my original I read"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ano", "text_ar": "اَنْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as meaning"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "liy^al~aA", "text_ar": "لِيَلَّا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] he should execute his desire upon thee: pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazaAy^imu", "text_ar": "عَزَايِمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EazaAy^imu", "text_ar": "عَزَايِمُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "charms,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "spells,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that are recited"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for the cure of diseases,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]: or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text":